Please read That you want from me box before requesting!
I'm gonna less-active soon, because my company moves to somewhere far away. Anyway I'll do my job but it can be kinda late.

Ask.fm / Twitter / Steam / YouTube


What I have to do

https://osu.ppy.sh/b/921164https://osu.ppy.sh/s/565779
Can't take more than this now!

Ongoing

https://osu.ppy.sh/s/594867
That you want from me
Hello! thank you for considering me to icon your map, unfortunately, I have a job now so I'm very busy these days and can't catch up to all the request people have for me. I work very hard to help mappers get their maps checked but I wont be able to check them all because of how busy I am with life, recently, I have been very stressed about modding and just want to kinda relax and play osu for a bit, we are here to help but we are not your slaves so please consider asking someone other than me if you can.

  • Discord : Fresh Chicken#6125 = Contact me on Discord if you have some question or requests.

  1. Do not request in-game. Recently, I can't even enjoy / play this game due to a lot of requests. So please don't.
  2. Forum PM is fine, but you should follow this format.
    Get a PM icon what icon you need.
    Map's link and bloodcat link if it has. But if it doesn't, you don't have to, but you have to say that this map don't have bloodcat links.
    What key your mapset have.
    SR
  3. "What I have to do"'s max slot is 3, so check it carefully before you request to me.
  4. I personally support something unique mapset. But notespam, overmapping, just harder map are never unique mapset.
  5. Sometimes I will say this "Get a bubble from other BNs, then I will qualify." Which means I'm not sure about your map or have no time. But that is not rejecting, so don't worry.
  6. I noticed in recent that mappers can't go rank their harder maps because of a new BN rule (You are not allowed to nominate maps that you can not judge properly). So if you have problem with this, let me know. I will quickly check your map first, and will let you know that I can judge this map or not. But your map must have a enough quality in my subjective opinion.


I never take request in weekdays.

Do not hurry for your map, there's nothing change even if you rank your map slowly. This one be able to cancel BN checking.

If you ignore this rules or just push me again and again, I'll just block you and won't take request FOREVER.


Thanks to Kawawa ,- Magic Bomb -, Soul Evans for supporters!!


Joined Beatmap Nominator Group in 31 May 2016. Thanks for supporting me!
